From cf472e9d7a8791a93698b7ff4945631e1797577d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Steve <steventhanhtuan@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 14:39:45 +0700
Subject: [PATCH 06/17] task4: verification core, verify_note + Verdict in
 coral/hub/publication.py

Cited attempt must exist (short-hash prefix resolution), be a real
scored attempt by the note's own creator, and every quoted evidence
score must match the recorded one (tol 5e-5). Refuted notes with valid
evidence stay verified but demote to low confidence; an evidence
mismatch overrides the refuted path. Unverifiable (no or in-flight
evidence) is distinct from failed. score_delta deliberately unchecked.

Reviewed; regression tests mutation-checked. 657 passed, ruff clean.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
